Marek: Psychological help
The proposed plan is a good idea according to the main economist of Patria Finance David Marek, but implementation will be very difficult.
"This is because you do not know what mechanism and the price of the problem assets are being purchased.
This will be crucial for how the financial sector and government split the losses among themselves, "said Marek to the server iHNed.cz. this week
Whether the plan is adopted now or at the beginning of next week, Marek's view is not decisive.
"It is much more important that the congressmen agree to support the plan and that they adopt it as soon as possible.
The psychological importance of the agreement on the adoption of the agreement is at this moment the most important, "said Marek.
